attributes.magic: PE32 executable (GUI) Intel 80386, for MS Windows

sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects suspicious start of rundll32.exe without any parameters as found in CobaltStrike beacon activity
Detects the presence of the keywords "Wscript", "Shell" and "Run" in the command, which could indicate a suspicious activity

sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Rundll32 Execution With Uncommon DLL Extension
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects the execution of rundll32 with a command line that doesn't contain a common extension
sigma_analysis_results.rule_author: Tim Shelton, Florian Roth (Nextron Systems), Yassine Oukessou

threat_severity.level_description: Severity HIGH because it was considered trojan. Other contributing factor was that it could not be run in sandboxes.

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert ( gid:119; sid:9; rev: 2; msg:"(http_inspect) backslash used in URI path"; metadata: rule-type preproc; service:http; classtype:not-suspicious;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: ET INFO DNS Query for Suspicious .ml Domain
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert dns $HOME_NET any -> any any (msg:"ET INFO DNS Query for Suspicious .ml Domain"; threshold: type limit, count 1, track by_src, seconds 120; dns.query; content:".ml"; nocase; endswith; classtype:bad-unknown; sid:2025106; rev:4; metadata:created_at 2017_12_03, former_category HUNTING, updated_at 2020_09_16;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: ET INFO DNS Query for Suspicious .ml Domain
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert dns $HOME_NET any -> any any (msg:"ET INFO DNS Query for Suspicious .ml Domain"; threshold: type limit, count 1, track by_src, seconds 120; dns.query; content:".ml"; nocase; endswith; classtype:misc-activity; sid:2025106; rev:6; metadata:created_at 2017_12_03, signature_severity Informational, updated_at 2022_12_01;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: ET INFO Suspicious Domain (*.ml) in TLS SNI
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert tls $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET any (msg:"ET INFO Suspicious Domain (*.ml) in TLS SNI"; flow:established,to_server; threshold: type limit, count 1, track by_src, seconds 120; tls.sni; content:".ml"; endswith; fast_pattern; nocase; classtype:misc-activity; sid:2025110; rev:6; metadata:created_at 2017_12_03, signature_severity Informational, updated_at 2022_12_01;)

alert udp $HOME_NET any -> any 53 ( msg:"INDICATOR-COMPROMISE Suspicious .ml dns query"; flow:to_server; byte_test:1,!&,0xF8,2; content:"|02|ml|00|",fast_pattern,nocase; metadata:policy max-detect-ips drop,policy security-ips drop; service:dns; reference:url,en.wikipedia.org/wiki/.ml; classtype:misc-activity; sid:39866; rev:4; )
